OL,3,CEnergy companies to be forced to offer
OL,4,Clow or no standing charge tariffs
OL,6,FEnergy supplies will be forced to
OL,7,Foffer tariffs with low or no standing
OL,8,Fcharges after complaints that they
OL,9,Fpunish people who try their hardest to
OL,10,Fuse minimal gas and electricity.
OL,12,FOfgem said it is consulting on
OL,13,Fbringing in the option under the price
OL,14,Fcap that would cover so-called zero
OL,15,Fstanding charge tariffs.
OL,17,FThe watchdog said it wants the tariffs
OL,18,Fto be available in time for winter
OL,19,F2025.
