OL,3,CEnergy companies to be forced to offer
OL,4,Clow or no standing charge tariffs
OL,6,FStanding charges are applied daily,
OL,7,Fregardless of how much energy the
OL,8,Fcustomer uses, and are used to cover
OL,9,Fthe cost of supplying energy to homes
OL,10,Fand businesses.
OL,12,FThey also cover the costs of building
OL,13,Fnew network infrastructure and keeping
OL,14,Fthe power on when energy suppliers go
OL,15,Fbust.
OL,17,FBut campaigners say they are unfair
OL,18,Fbecause everybody pays the same rate,
OL,19,Fmeaning they make up a far higher
OL,20,Fproportion of bills for people using
OL,21,Fless energy.
