OL,3,CEnergy companies to be forced to offer
OL,4,Clow or no standing charge tariffs
OL,6,FCharlotte Friel, director for retail
OL,7,Fpricing and systems at Ofgem, said:
OL,8,F"We know from the huge response we've
OL,9,Fhad that many feel standing charges
OL,10,Fare unfair.
OL,12,F"However, we also know that
OL,13,Fvulnerable, high-energy users `
OL,14,Fincluding those who rely on medical
OL,15,Fequipment at home or low-income
OL,16,Ffamilies in poorly insulated houses `
OL,17,Fwould suffer disproportionately if
OL,18,Fthese costs were added to the unit
OL,19,Frate for everyone.
