OL,3,CEnergy companies to be forced to offer
OL,4,Clow or no standing charge tariffs
OL,6,F"That's why we're moving forward with
OL,7,Fplans that will give customers a
OL,8,Fchoice and more control over how they
OL,9,Fchoose to pay for their gas and
OL,10,Felectricity.
OL,12,F"We're looking closely at how these
OL,13,Ftariffs will work in practice, but
OL,14,Feveryone will need to carefully
OL,15,Fconsider which option best suits their
OL,16,Fneeds.
