OL,11,FHe said Ofgem should move vulnerable
OL,12,Fcustomers who do not use much
OL,13,Felectricity to a "low or no standing
OL,14,Fcharge" tariff by default, using an
OL,15,Fopt-out mechanism, so that people do
OL,16,Fnot miss out on savings.
