OL,6,FChief executive Dhara Vyas said the
OL,7,Fplan would "increase the challenges
OL,8,Fand risks" associated with buying
OL,9,Fenergy in advance for power firms.
OL,11,FAnd it could increase the "complexity"
OL,12,Ffor consumers, she added, because
OL,13,Fpeople would have to make "an active
OL,14,Fchoice" about which tariff to be on
OL,15,Fand could end up on the wrong plan.
